{"article_id":"DOyzuS1yPWOynV9c","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"( CNN ) -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"A national ban on assault weapons may have met all-but-certain death in the Senate this week ,","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"but one of the measure ' s proponents","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"- New York City Mayor Michael Bloomberg -","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"said Sunday","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"his fight wasn ' t over .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"\" I do n't think","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"there 's ever been an issue","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"where the public has spoken so clearly ,","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"where Congress has n't eventually understood","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"and done the right thing , \"","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"Bloomberg said on NBC ' s \" Meet the Press . \"","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"Earlier this week , Senate Majority Leader Harry Reid left off the ban on assault weapons","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"when he introduced gun control legislation in the upper chamber .","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"The measure would expand background checks ,","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"improve school safety","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"and restrict gun trafficking .","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"The assault weapons ban ,","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"which was introduced by Sen. Dianne Feinstein , D-California ,","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"will be voted on as an amendment to the larger gun control bill .","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"It ' s not expected to gain approval in the full Senate .","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"But","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"despite the ban ' s demise ,","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"Bloomberg said","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"part of his goal","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"- having the Senate vote on the measure -","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"will be met .","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"\" We demanded a plan","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"and then we demanded a vote .","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"We have the plan .","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"We 're going to get the vote .","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"It 's incumbent on us to make our voices heard , \"","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"Bloomberg said ,","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"adding","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"he thought","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"eventually a ban would succeed in Congress .","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"\" We have a lot of work ahead of us .","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"I do n't think","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"we should give up on the assault weapons ban .","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"But clearly it is a more difficult issue for a lot of people , \"","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"On Saturday , Bloomberg ' s anti-gun violence group announced","depth":5},{"id":42,"text":"it was spending another $ 12 million","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"to air ads","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"putting pressure on Republican and Democratic lawmakers","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"to vote for tighter gun control laws .","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"The group , Mayors Against Illegal Guns , had already spent tens of millions on previous ads .","depth":4},{"id":47,"text":"The television push amounts to Bloomberg trying \" to impose his will on the American public , \"","depth":5},{"id":48,"text":"according to Wayne LaPierre , the executive vice president of the National Rifle Association .","depth":5},{"id":49,"text":"\" They don ' t want him in their restaurants ,","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"they don ' t want him in their homes ,","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"they don ' t want him telling what food to eat .","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"They sure don ' t want him telling what self-defense firearms to own .","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"He can ' t buy America , \"","depth":6},{"id":54,"text":"LaPierre said , also on NBC .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":109,"left":0,"right":108,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":108,"left":94,"right":107,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"